    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Work on the addition Of a new\nstory to Central Labor hall will prob\nably begin the middle of next month.\nSenator Turner has agreed to enlarge\nthe building at the request Of the\ntrades council, as at present it is\nunable to accommodate all the unions\naffiliated with the central body."
